room_title: Escape room "A Haunting at Winchester Manor" by Tri-State Escape in Huntington
room_description: You have been summonsed to the home of your late great-grandfather for a reading of his will and have been forewarned that some strange things have been happening at the residence. Crunched for time, you hope to get in, get your inheritance, and get out as quickly as possible. Will it be that simple, or will 1327 Winchester Avenue become your permanent home?
